title: Catalonia independence voters clash with Spanish police
description:
The leader of the Spanish region of Catalonia says it has won the right to become its own state, after a highly contentious referendum saw 90% of voters back independence. The day was marred by violence with Spanish police accused of being heavy handed.

Spain's Prime Minister said the referendum made a "mockery" of democracy.
tags: News', 'Catalonia', 'Catalonia referendum', 'Catalonia independence', 'Catalonia independence referendum', 'Catalonia Spain'
